    "::: {.gray-container}\n",
    "\n",
    "**Lesson Objective:** In this lesson, you will learn how to use the Python programming language to calculate summary statistics and investigate nitrates and nitrates in water quality samples.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Materials Needed:**  \n",
    "- Your computer  \n",
    "- A web browser (Chrome, Firefox, or Safari)  \n",
    "- A calculator   \n",
    "- Printed handout (including lab sheet)\n",
    ":::\n",
    "\n",
    ":::{.ltblue-container}\n",
    "**Checkpoints on this Page:**\n",
    "\n",
