    "- [**Checkpoint 2:** Mathematical Operators](#lst-mathoperators)\n",
    "- [**Checkpoint 3:** Comparing Values](#lst-comparingvalues)\n",
    "- [**Checkpoint 4:** Print Statements with Math](#lst-printstatementsmath)\n",
